title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: There is virtually zero chance of anybody sneaking an item from their own agenda onto your list of priorities today. You are operating according to what matters to you and arent likely to be shy about letting others know that polite requests will be considered now, but pushy demands rejected. Confidence radiates from your very pores when reasonable boundaries protect your schedule. Jazz icon Miles Davis said, Time isnt the main thing. Its the only thing. Own yours like a boss. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
